## Authentication & Authorization
- REST endpoints require valid session cookie (existing auth middleware)
- WebSocket requires auth token in query param: `/api/ws?token=xxx`
- Benchmark trigger requires admin role (checked via session)
- All requests include `X-Request-ID` header for tracing

## Rate Limiting
- History endpoint: 60 requests/minute per session
- Trigger endpoint: 1 per worker per 5 minutes (bypassed with force=true, admin only)
- WebSocket: 100 messages/minute per connection

